_sText:
It took me a little while to build this map. It is my first CS:S map.
There is a secret teleport in the map that leads to the top of the map, good for sniping, and it is up to you to figure out where it is. There are some good spots for camping, and knifing too. I dont know what else to say, So i hope you enjoy!

NOTE: Please give feedback or suggestions on the map so that I can make it better. Thanks.
